# `Map` — key-to-value lookup

## Same three flavours as `Set`

- **`HashMap`** unordered · **`LinkedHashMap`** insertion order · **`TreeMap`** sorted keys

```java
ages.getOrDefault("dan", 0);          // fallback
ages.merge("alice", 1, Integer::sum); // += 1
ages.computeIfAbsent("eve", k -> 0);
```

- Iterate `keySet()` · `values()` · `entrySet()`
